msgid "Mesh Protocol"
msgstr "Mesh协议"

msgid "802.11s native: kernel-level forwarding, simpler setup. batman-adv: advanced L2 routing on top of 802.11s, better multi-hop performance. When switching modes, save and reboot all nodes."
